N_n
 X_i = \{(D,E,F) : D \subseteq N_n, |D| = r,E\subseteq D, |E|=r-i,F\subseteq N_n - D, |F|=s-i\} 
|X_0 \cup X_1 \cup \ldots\cup X_n| = \sum_{i=0}^n  \binom{n}{r}\binom{r}{r-i}\binom{n-r}{s-i}
X_i
 \begin{align} |X_0 \cup X_1 \cup \ldots\cup X_n| &=\sum_{i=0}^n|X_i|\\ &= \dots \end{align} 
X_i
\binom{n}{r}=\frac{n!}{r!(n-r)!}
D
\binom{r}{r-i}=\frac{r!}{(r-i)!(r-(r-i))!}
E
\binom{n-r}{s-i}=\frac{(n-r)!}{(s-i)!(n-r-(s-i))!}
F
|X_i|=\binom{n}{r}\binom{r}{r-i}\binom{n-r}{s-i}
|X_0 \cup X_1 \cup \ldots\cup X_n| =\sum_{i=0}^n|X_i|=\sum_{i=0}^n \binom{n}{r}\binom{r}{r-i}\binom{n-r}{s-i}
